display_title = "The Vault"
text = "The Sisters don't keep lights in their vault, but there is an actinic glow that suffuses the room. With it, you perceive the heaps of canvas-wrapped objects massed against the walls like trash in an attic. You wonder for a moment what other treasures the Sisters have hoarded here. What other Hours are being disgraced here? 

But you are here for a purpose. For the Watchman. To prove that none of His treasures can be hidden for long.

You stumble past the rarities to the very end of the room, where the glow is strongest. There is an altar, a box, a heavy tapestry from under which the the cobalt light leaks..."
